 & =\lim_{h\rightarrow0}\frac{3x^{2}+6xh+h^{2}-3x^{2}}{h}\\
 & =\lim_{h\rightarrow0}\frac{6xh+h^{2}}{h}=\lim_{h\rightarrow0}\frac{h\left(6x+h\right)}{h}\\
 & =\lim_{h\rightarrow0}\left(6x+h\right)=6x.
\end{align*}

\end_inset

Entonces, la derivada de 
\begin_inset Formula $f\left(x\right)=3x^{2}$
\end_inset

